{"word":"H6775 - צָמַד - tsâmad - tsaw-mad' - Fasten","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָמַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tsâmad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-mad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fasten"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பற்றிக்கொள், தொங்கு. பிணை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to bind, to join, to fasten"},{"paragraph":"a) (Niphal) to join, to join or to attach oneself to"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be fastened, to be bound"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to combine, to fit together, to hitch up"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>link</i>, that is, <i>gird</i>; figuratively to <i>serve</i>, (mentally) <i>contrive: - </i>fasten, frame, join (self)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6775 - צָמַד - tsâmad - tsaw-mad'/6775\">H6775</a>, <a href=\"#/H6776 - צֶמֶד - tsemed - tseh'-med/6776\">H6776</a>, <a href=\"#/H6781 - צָמִיד - tsâmîyd - tsaw-meed'/6781\">H6781</a>"}]}